Change discount to 50 percent

$quantity = (int)$cart_product['quantity'];
$new_product_price = $new_product_price - ($product_price * 0.5 * floor($quantity / 2));

And update the subtotal variable:

$subtotal += $new_product_price;

Add the new code to the "cart.php" and "checkout.php" files. On line 137 in cart.php and line 98 in checkout.php.



